Package com.hemebiotech.analytics

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InterfaceSymptomCounter
    From a list of all Symptoms.
    InterfaceSymptomReader
    From a file "symptom.txt" of Symptoms, it will read line per line and return a list of strings.
    InterfaceSymptomWriter
    From a TreeMap of Symptoms and their occurrences sort in ascending order.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnalyticsCounter
    AnalyticsCounter main class of the project is build to read file "symptom.txt" including Symptoms and to write out alphabetically all Symptoms and their occurrences.
    SymptomCounter
    Simple brute force implementation of InterfaceSymptomCounter.
    SymptomReader
    Simple brute force implementation of InterfaceSymptomReader.
    SymptomWriter
    Simple brute force implementation of InterfaceSymptomWriter.
